    <h2>Aniq artikllar: "El" va "La"</h2>
    
    <div class="example-box">
        <h3>"El" – erkak jinsdagi (masculino) otlar oldida</h3>
        <p><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">El</span> – bu aniq artikl bo‘lib, erkak jinsdagi (masculino) otlar oldida ishlatiladi. Gapiruvchi va eshituvchi biladi: qaysi erkak haqida gap ketayapti.</p>
        
        <p><span class="sp-word" data-tr="U (erkak)">Él</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="yeydi">come</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="non">pan</span>. – U (erkak) non yeydi.</p>
        <p>Gapiruvchi va eshituvchi biladi: qaysi erkak non yeyapti.</p>
        
        <p><span class="sp-word" data-tr="U (erkak)">Él</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="ichadi">bebe</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="suv">agua</span>. – U (erkak) suv ichadi.</p>
        
        <p><span class="sp-word" data-tr="U (erkak)">Él</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="o'rganadi">estudia</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="ispan tili">español</span>. – U (erkak) ispan tilini o‘rganadi.</p>
        
        <p>"<span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">El</span>" artikli faqat erkak jinsidagi otlar bilan ishlatiladi: <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="erkak">hombre</span> (erkak), <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="it">perro</span> (it), <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="kitob">libro</span> (kitob).</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="example-box">
        <h3>"La" – ayol jinsdagi (femenino) otlar oldida</h3>
        <p><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Ayol artikl (aniq)">La</span> – bu ayol jinsdagi (femenino) otlar oldida ishlatiladigan aniq artikl. Gapiruvchi va eshituvchi biladi: qaysi ayol haqida gap ketayapti.</p>
        
        <p><span class="sp-word" data-tr="U (qiz)">La niña</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="yeydi">come</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="non">pan</span>. – U (qiz) non yeydi.</p>
        <p>Gapiruvchi va eshituvchi biladi: qaysi qiz non yeyapti.</p>
        
        <p><span class="sp-word" data-tr="U (qiz)">La niña</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="ichadi">bebe</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="suv">agua</span>. – U (qiz) suv ichadi.</p>
        
        <p><span class="sp-word" data-tr="U (qiz)">La niña</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="o'rganadi">estudia</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="ispan tili">español</span>. – U (qiz) ispan tilini o‘rganadi.</p>
        
        <p>"<span class="sp-word" data-tr="Ayol artikl (aniq)">La</span>" artikli faqat ayol jinsidagi otlar bilan ishlatiladi: <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Ayol artikl (aniq)">la</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="ayol">mujer</span> (ayol), <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Ayol artikl (aniq)">la</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="mushuk (ayol)">gata</span> (mushuk-ayol), <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Ayol artikl (aniq)">la</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="uy">casa</span> (uy).</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="eslatma">
        <p><strong>Eslatma:</strong> "<span class="sp-word" data-tr="U (erkak)">Él</span>" (u - erkak) va "<span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span>" (artikl) bir-biriga o'xshash, lekin farqli so'zlar! "<span class="sp-word" data-tr="U (erkak)">Él</span>" urg'u bilan yoziladi va olmosh, "<span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span>" esa urg'usiz va artikl.</p>
    </div>
    
    <hr>
    
    <h3>Qoidalarga Istisnolar (Esda saqlang!)</h3>
    <p>Har doim ham qoida ishlamaydi. Eng ko‘p uchraydigan istisnolar:</p>
    
    <div class="istisno">
        <p><strong>1. -a bilan tugab, erkak jinsidagi otlar:</strong> Ba'zi otlar -a bilan tugasa ham, erkak jinsiga kiradi va <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> artiklini oladi.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="kun">día</span> (kun)</li>
            <li><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="xarita">mapa</span> (xarita)</li>
            <li><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="muammo">problema</span> (muammo)</li>
            <li><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="tizim">sistema</span> (tizim)</li>
            <li><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="iqlim">clima</span> (iqlim)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>2. -o bilan tugab, ayol jinsidagi otlar:</strong> Juda kam uchraydi, lekin <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Ayol artikl (aniq)">la</span> artiklini oladi.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Ayol artikl (aniq)">la</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="qo'l">mano</span> (qo‘l)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>3. Qisqa so'zlar va urg'uli "a" bilan boshlangan ayol jinsidagi otlar:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="suv">agua</span> (suv) - Aslida ayol jinsidagi so'z (<span class="sp-word" data-tr="suv">agua</span> <span class="sp-word" data-tr="sovuq">fría</span>), lekin urg'uli "a" tufayli <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> artiklini oladi.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <hr>
    
    <h3>Xulosa va Eslatma</h3>
    <p>Ispan tilida yangi so‘z yodlaganda, uni artikli bilan birga yod oling.</p>
    
    <div class="yaxshi-yomon">
        <p><span style="color: #ff6666;">✗ Yomon yodlash:</span> libro, casa, puente.</p>
        <p><span style="color: #66ff66;">✓ Yaxshi yodlash:</span> 
            <strong>
                <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> 
                <span class="sp-word" data-tr="kitob">libro</span>, 
                <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Ayol artikl (aniq)">la</span> 
                <span class="sp-word" data-tr="uy">casa</span>, 
                <span class="sp-word" data-tr="Erkak artikl (aniq)">el</span> 
                <span class="sp-word" data-tr="ko'prik">puente</span>
            </strong>.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Agar so‘zni artikli bilan yodlasangiz, kelajakda sifat va olmoshlarni to‘g‘ri qo‘llash siz uchun oson bo‘ladi.</p>

